#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.ranf.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.random.ranf"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.random_sample.random_sample:1 of
msgid "Return random floats in the half-open interval [0.0, 1.0)."
msgstr "返回半开区间 [0.0, 1.0) 内的随机浮点数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.random_sample.random_sample:3 of
msgid ""
"Results are from the \"continuous uniform\" distribution over the stated "
"interval.  To sample :math:`Unif[a, b), b > a` multiply the output of "
"`random_sample` by `(b-a)` and add `a`::"
msgstr ""
"结果来自指定区间的“连续均匀”分布。要从 :math:`Unif[a, b), b > a` 中采样"
"，可以将 `random_sample` 的输出乘以 `(b-a)` 并加上 `a`："

#: maxframe.tensor.random.random_sample.random_sample of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.random_sample.random_sample:9 of
msgid ""
"Output shape.  If the given shape is, e.g., ``(m, n, k)``, then ``m * n *"
" k`` samples are drawn.  Default is None, in which case a single value is"
" returned."
msgstr ""
"输出形状。如果给定形状，例如 ``(m, n, k)``，则抽取 ``m * n * k`` 个样本。"
"默认为 None，此时返回单个值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.random_sample.random_sample:13 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上期望的块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.random_sample.random_sample:15 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True，则在 GPU 上分配张量，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.random_sample.random_sample:17 of
msgid "Data-type of the returned tensor."
msgstr "返回张量的数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.random_sample.random_sample of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.random_sample.random_sample:20 of
msgid ""
"**out** -- Array of random floats of shape `size` (unless ``size=None``, "
"in which case a single float is returned)."
msgstr ""
"**out** -- 形状为 `size` 的随机浮点数组（除非 ``size=None``，此时返回单个"
"浮点数）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.random_sample.random_sample of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.random_sample.random_sample:25 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.random_sample.random_sample:35 of
msgid "Three-by-two array of random numbers from [-5, 0):"
msgstr "从 [-5, 0) 中抽取的 3 行 2 列的随机数数组："

